illin, Carbenicillin, Bacampicillin, Ticarcillin, Mezlocillin, Tazobactam, Cloxacillin, More', 'Diamorphine, Acamprosate, Lofexidine, Naltrexone, Varenicline, Disulfiram, Nalmefene, Nicotine', 1767369485);
